Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.54,Castle Fantasia main@,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Year 158 of the New Common Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:09.86,Castle Fantasia main@,,0,0,0,,{\be1}On Synapse Continent, the conflict known as the Holy Demon Wars has broken out again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:15.24,Castle Fantasia main@,,0,0,0,,{\be1}according to legends passed down, \Nit is not just a conflict of demons and people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:20.86,Castle Fantasia main@,,1,1,0,,{\be1}Two hundred years have passed since war broke out, and on the side fighting for a bright future, a single hero has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:27.27,Castle Fantasia main@,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This story takes place during the time of this hero and tells also of the many dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:36.76,DESU Presents,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\pos(307,70)}SubDESU-H Presents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:36.76,Castle Fantasia Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(512,448)}Holy Demon Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:36.76,Castle Fantasia Title3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(376,542)}Chapter Three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:42.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The victorious Ingela Army was at Eberuzado, the largest field of battle in the Holy Demon Wars, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:48.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}due to heavy casualties, they postponed further advancement for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:54.27,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Reinforcements from unit 8 were sent to the fortress at Arubidabu, to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:01.06,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I suppose this is our only choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:05.55,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ducis, Hewie, just now, for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:10.99,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}could you go along with this selfish, doddering old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:20.38,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.93,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The number four unit on the front line will advance as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.63,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The number one unit will return to Parumira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:30.79,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The number seven unit will, together with the newly-formed number eight unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:34.84,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}encircle Arubidabur fort's defensive outpost and assume responsibility for subjugating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:36.11,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.51,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We will faithfully carry out the imperial orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.78,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That is all. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:41.75,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.51,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I have great hopes for you, Somia. {I split this line so it wasn't sponsored by the "department of redundancy department" :P}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:59.45,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Leed, your daughter has grown into a strong adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.58,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I will definitely keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:05.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I will show you Somia rising above all others as a fine holy knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.60,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Come back alive, and let's go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.42,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course. Take care of yourself on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.29,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, yes. Watch out for the number eight unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.63,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There have been various dark rumors about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:23.00,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's fine. You, too, take care of your new wife, Carraway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:23.82,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.34,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.92,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ducis-sama is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.84,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Mm, yeah, he had imperial orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He's leaving tomorrow, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:45.08,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I-I-I-I'm going to go pay him my respects! Renoir, you come with me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.80,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Even so, pulling the number one unit from the front line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:55.07,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and leaving just the number four unit, capturing Kurikara and Estancion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:03:00.10,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I've had it! On top of that, left together with that shady unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.96,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}They are an established unit fighting for the same side. You shouldn't be that prejudiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.72,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.89,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It’s THE number eight unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:10.69,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Number eight, the 'massacre' unit. Rumors are spreading among the commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's just a baseless rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.00,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Besides, for tomorrow's operation to be a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.58,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}we've been ordered to deal with the remnants of Luciole's garrison,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.33,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,20,,{\be1}who appear to be hiding out in a small village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:26.62,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}First thing tomorrow morning, meet with the tactician over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.43,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Commander, does it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.46,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:54.59,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Then, next, stand up, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.23,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sorry... it just felt too good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.94,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:35.45,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Could you make sure everything goes well with the number eight unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.80,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If it matters that much to you, Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.19,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.64,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hewie-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:51.93,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.44,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The stars were just too pretty, so I accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:57.50,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.04,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tonight's Ciruela is very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.55,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The coming military action is becoming far too unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.52,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Even though the enemy is right before our eyes, it's as if their intentions are shrouded in fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.39,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The return of the number one unit's desperate effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If would be nice if our infiltrator behind the scenes could find something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:34.36,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, Hewie-sama, more, more, stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.91,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The commander is... in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:04.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ciruela...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:41.43,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm cumming, I'm going to cum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.24,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm counting on you to look after the place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.97,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Will I not be of use?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.08,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:04.14,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To the extent that all other units are ordered forth, you won't take part in this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:08.39,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Besides, I want to leave this task to the most trustworthy subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.44,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.70,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.44,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Because you have so much faith in me, I will do my absolute best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.03,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.00,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Finally, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.12,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The resistance was a lot more violent than we were expecting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.93,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Commander! We've got trouble! Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.16,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,20,,{\be1}{\an8}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.40,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}C-C-Cecile is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:03.42,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, hey, Ciruela, what's a 'secret unit'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}'Secret unit'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:10.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I heard it mentioned over there. They said that Somia was a 'secret unit'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:16.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A secret unit is a military tactic where someone infiltrates the enemy forces and gathers information,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.40,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}assassinating important people if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:23.78,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's a special unit under orders from military headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.29,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Really? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.17,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:33.89,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}They collude with the enemy and inflict punishment on traitors as emergency measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:40.41,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If you become part of a secret unit, you supposedly can't stop until you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.24,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}She's a holy knight, and what's more, a commanding officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.97,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Move! Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.55,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I refuse. What did you say these people did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}They are all victims of the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.63,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hiding enemy weapons is a serious crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.27,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's why we're going to sentence them here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.76,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}So the rumors were actually true, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.46,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Unit eight, a 'massacre' unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.24,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}These are all traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Traitors must... traitors must...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:22.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.53,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.31,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don't kill the commoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.91,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's not in your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.16,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The battle is already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you okay, Cecile?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.49,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.46,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's unusual to see you so flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.13,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}N-Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.48,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's just that I didn't want to see people not involved in the war die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:06.15,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, so that's what you're like underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.18,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You have such a pretty smile, so why do you wear sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.01,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.07,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm going to ensure the safety of the injured commoners and then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.60,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Removing me from command?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.72,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was only thinking about punishing traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.05,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And that I have to be punished for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.09,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}HE is the one who should be discharged!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.52,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:40.30,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Raising your sword against civilians is an act of heresy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.88,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You should be grateful to Hewie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You have no grounds to criticize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.97,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Heresy, you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.12,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:04.34,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As I thought, I'm no substitute for a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.81,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What have you come to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.09,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To look at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.40,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Looking at the stars, I can feel humanity's insignificance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:39.48,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do you live for? Why do you keep on going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:51.61,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}From before we're born, until after we're dead and gone, the stars continue to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:00.81,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:07.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I thought you’d say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.51,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well, I'm going to take a bath and wash away the day's sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.73,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.43,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Mind... your own business...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.57,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
