Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.47,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Not like you, Cecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.02,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.30,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Involving the innocent people of that village in the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:07.69,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Your eyes were beautiful then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.18,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Very clear, and a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.64,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:20.56,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I think deep down you have undeniable strength... and purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:25.39,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm really glad I have subordinates like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:26.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How far were you planning to follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.54,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was planning on taking my bath alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}do you want to come in with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.63,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes! As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.47,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you okay? You're not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.90,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}J-Just... be gentle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.77,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.11,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.29,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You get aroused pretty easily.
