Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's why it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:14.30,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.78,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was just given this.
