Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.07,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This... What on earth is the King thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.58,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Forming an alliance with those demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.35,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh dear, you learned the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.54,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That old man is so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.44,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Wh-Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.60,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If you butt in too far, you might get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.38,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.56,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.42,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.84,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.58,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Why did my father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:36.05,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}For your father, become a fine holy knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.63,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Commander! {*the term was “Shireikan” which literally means “official who gives orders”…find a better English word for this} {Wouldn't that be a commander though?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You did this to the Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}N-No, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:49.62,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:00.51,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It wasn't me! He was dead when I came in! I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:00.80,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,20,,{\be1}{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.78,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:05.10,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You lie. Didn't you have an argument with the general?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.83,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just the sort of thing a beginner in the secret troops would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.14,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You even went so far as to kill your commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:13.26,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You just sit there quietly and think about your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}On top of being deprived of your command, the death penalty is more than likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:30.06,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Father... did I... make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.67,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How're you? Feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:44.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Idiot. I've been imprisoned on a false charge. How the hell could I be feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:49.42,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course... You think I did this, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:57.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There's circumstantial evidence from the place of the crime, but there's no physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.29,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The weapon used for the murder is too heavy for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.47,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.04,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How about it? I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You really are something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.08,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.48,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's to protect your dead father's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.32,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The only thing I was able to get from my father was his blood as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:29.92,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As a daughter in a job I couldn't abandon, with just my blood to rely on, I couldn't match my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's a big sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.54,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:37.46,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m just obsessed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:43.09,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Those of us in the secret unit, no matter how hard we work, are never recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.40,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We continue to take on jobs that the other units despise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As a result, by mistake you've become known as the 'massacre' unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.58,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Your sentence has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.75,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.98,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I supposedly murdered my father’s best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.32,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:14.66,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The council of the military court didn't allow for a formal trial, and made their decision arbitrarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.13,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And I was appointed the executioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.26,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:22.32,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course, I plan to refuse. The decision was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.54,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Why are you angry about it? You're a strange person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:30.21,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Besides, it's funny, but I think it would feel good to have you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.07,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.08,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's just... If there was one thing I’d regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What would you regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:44.82,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}... It would be to die without knowing the feel of lying with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.66,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.20,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you being honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:58.49,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I suppose. Lying with an interesting guy like you wouldn't be half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:00.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}All right. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:27.69,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:41.67,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.93,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}H-Hewie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.85,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just a little more, lower your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:50.39,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:52.41,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re so…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:55.67,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:22:58.99,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.70,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, I see. Somia, you're getting aroused here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:04.65,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Down there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:17.96,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:19.66,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:22.44,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}... Thrusting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:35.82,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hewie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:37.08,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:40.03,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's my first time, so be gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:43.59,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don't worry. You have good instincts, so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.56,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Th-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.82,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes... Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.65,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm... almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:31.35,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hewie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.02,0:24:33.91,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm cumming! I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.66,0:24:57.79,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}She's escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.54,0:25:02.56,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Search over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.73,0:25:04.89,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Could she have gone there...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:05.41,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Is she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.71,0:25:06.25,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.88,0:25:09.78,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Having done that, I truly am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:12.71,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But I really couldn't kill Somia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.25,0:25:17.69,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As the time came closer, I felt doubts about this country's justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.67,0:25:22.86,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The powerful people are naturally running roughshod over the laws I've held since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:24.79,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's something I simply cannot allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:29.84,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's why I can't throw away lives fighting for this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.41,0:25:33.27,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And for the same reason, I cannot order my subordinates to do so either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.86,0:25:37.96,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You must be wondering why I left you girls behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.16,0:25:42.74,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's because, as regular soldiers, you form a private army.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.35,0:25:44.66,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hewie-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.81,0:25:54.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If we're lucky, we might be able to meet again sometime. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.52,0:25:58.24,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:01.05,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Doing something like this for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:07.19,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No matter what I do, I'm unfit to be a holy knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.51,0:26:08.87,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It was a perfect chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:10.59,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What are you going to do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:14.47,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Are you just running away without thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.55,0:26:17.65,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hewie, you're going to marry me, and we'll have children,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.75,0:26:20.88,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and you'll make your own country, right, Hue-ba?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.02,0:26:22.03,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Country, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:27.59,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What a child you are! And besides, having a child is not that easy a thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.84,0:26:30.00,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's time for the second queen to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:31.70,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}S-Second queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:36.70,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My, my, you must be half asleep. The first queen is myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.13,0:26:40.29,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If you wish to become one of my followers, I may be so good as to allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.78,0:26:42.37,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.37,0:26:43.28,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:45.68,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.68,0:26:46.90,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:56.10,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Let's make a country. With our own hands. The ideal country.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:03.22,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.31,0:27:04.06,Castle Fantasia main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Giddyup!